871
00:56:16,754 --> 00:56:19,966
I swallowed some owls.
I won't charge you.

872
00:56:20,216 --> 00:56:21,467
Stop it!

873
00:56:23,219 --> 00:56:25,305
Give me that. Move.

874
00:56:26,431 --> 00:56:29,600
I'll take care of this.
We won't charge you. It's on us.

875
00:56:29,851 --> 00:56:31,394
I'll take care of it.

876
