893
00:58:14,998 --> 00:58:16,541
Thanksh Antoine.

894
00:58:16,916 --> 00:58:19,669
Your region is really very friendly.

895
00:58:19,919 --> 00:58:21,212
Maybe so,

896
00:58:21,462 --> 00:58:23,923
but with no one to welcome,
who cares?

897
00:58:24,173 --> 00:58:25,550
So we thank you.

898
00:58:25,800 --> 00:58:27,343
Don't mention it. Huh?

899
00:58:29,887 --> 00:58:31,556
There's a Shtimi proverb.

900
00:58:31,806 --> 00:58:35,143
When a stranger comes north
he brays twice.

901
00:58:35,393 --> 00:58:37,562
When he arrives and when he leaves.

902
00:58:38,813 --> 00:58:40,398
I was a bit down at first.

903
00:58:40,648 --> 00:58:42,400
Just wait till you leave!

904
00:58:44,736 --> 00:58:46,029
We'll shee.

905
00:58:46,279 --> 00:58:47,697
The south is my home.

906
00:58:47,947 --> 00:58:49,782
We'll shee.

907
00:58:55,163 --> 00:58:56,748
And 30.

908
00:58:58,499 --> 00:58:59,417
Bye, Ma'am.

909
00:58:59,667 --> 00:59:02,003
What do we have on for tonight?

910
00:59:03,838 --> 00:59:05,298
Sir, it's Friday.

911
00:59:05,548 --> 00:59:07,884
- Aren't you going home?
- To the shouth.

912
00:59:09,010 --> 00:59:10,053
Friday already?.

913
00:59:11,846 --> 00:59:13,139
Vandeus!

914
00:59:26,778 --> 00:59:28,279
Surprise!

915
00:59:29,697 --> 00:59:31,908
Your friends came to cheer you up.

916
00:59:32,367 --> 00:59:34,327
- Dad!
- Hey, little man.

917
00:59:37,622 --> 00:59:40,166
Julie told us how hard it is up there.

918
00:59:43,836 --> 00:59:47,548
When I open up it's still night.
Sunrise is at 1 1 :30.

919
00:59:47,799 --> 00:59:50,385
And at 5, boom!
Night falls again.

920
00:59:51,344 --> 00:59:55,014
They're all so...
All of them. Pale, white.

921
00:59:55,515 --> 00:59:57,016
They don't get much light.

922
00:59:57,266 --> 01:00:00,520
And the hygiene!
Last week, an epidemic started.

923
01:00:01,729 --> 01:00:03,439
Cholera.

924
01:00:07,860 --> 01:00:08,778
You got vaccinated?

925
01:00:09,445 --> 01:00:10,863
I'm going to have to.

926
01:00:11,114 --> 01:00:12,448
We'll check your boosters.

927
01:00:12,699 --> 01:00:14,117
It's worse than hell.

928
01:00:14,742 --> 01:00:17,328
Strange. I worked up north.
I have good memories.

929
01:00:32,093 --> 01:00:33,636
Next weekend in Belgium?

930
01:00:33,886 --> 01:00:35,096
Could be nice.

931
01:00:37,223 --> 01:00:38,433
I have to work.

932
01:00:39,350 --> 01:00:41,311
You don't like him seeing us?

933
01:00:41,561 --> 01:00:42,645
No, that's not it.

934
01:00:42,895 --> 01:00:44,022
So kish me.

935
01:00:44,272 --> 01:00:46,524
Don't be ridiculous.
See you tonight.

936
01:00:46,774 --> 01:00:48,234
- Kish me!
- That hurts!

937
01:00:48,609 --> 01:00:49,694
Problem, Annabelle?

938
01:00:50,320 --> 01:00:51,321
No, I'm fine.

939
01:00:51,654 --> 01:00:52,488
What is it, mailman?

940
01:00:52,989 --> 01:00:53,906
What you want?

941
01:00:54,198 --> 01:00:55,283
Got mail for me?

942
01:00:55,533 --> 01:00:56,784
Stop, Tony.

943
01:00:57,243 --> 01:00:58,953
No mail, but a text message.

944
01:00:59,203 --> 01:01:01,080
You can't read, so here it is.

945
01:01:01,372 --> 01:01:02,081
Stop.

946
01:01:03,666 --> 01:01:07,462
No parking in front of the post office.
Signed, Postman.

947
01:01:07,712 --> 01:01:09,297
Where's your mother?.

948
01:01:10,089 --> 01:01:11,299
Picking up after you?

949
01:01:13,092 --> 01:01:14,302
Stop it!

950
01:01:14,552 --> 01:01:15,845
Chime boy, want to fight?

951
01:01:16,095 --> 01:01:18,389
