1039
01:06:59,814 --> 01:07:02,025
It's a local specialty. Just taste.

1040
01:07:02,275 --> 01:07:03,860
It disinfects.

1041
01:07:04,444 --> 01:07:05,611
To your health!

1042
01:07:13,244 --> 01:07:14,912
Sugar takes the edge off.

1043
01:07:15,204 --> 01:07:16,080
Sugar?.

1044
01:07:17,790 --> 01:07:19,000
No sugar!

1045
01:07:26,215 --> 01:07:27,592
Thanks for the coffee.

1046
01:07:27,884 --> 01:07:28,885
Don't mention it.

1047
01:07:29,135 --> 01:07:31,137
Come back any time.

1048
01:07:31,387 --> 01:07:32,764
See you tomorrow.

1049
01:07:33,348 --> 01:07:35,016
Have a good day.

1050
01:07:41,105 --> 01:07:42,357
You see, Antoine,

1051
01:07:42,982 --> 01:07:45,818
how one can be cordial
with a customer,

1052
01:07:46,069 --> 01:07:47,779
while drinking only coffee.

1053
01:07:48,029 --> 01:07:49,238
Yes, I see.

1054
01:07:49,489 --> 01:07:50,448
But that's it!

1055
01:07:50,740 --> 01:07:51,783
There are limits!

1056
01:07:52,033 --> 01:07:54,952
- No more jennifer.
- Juniper.

1057
01:07:59,207 --> 01:08:02,627
Don't ring the bell!
They'll offer us a drink.

1058
01:08:02,960 --> 01:08:04,170
It's registered.

1059
01:08:04,420 --> 01:08:07,924
That's different.
But no going inside. No drinking.

1060
01:08:10,259 --> 01:08:11,010
Come in!

1061
01:08:11,260 --> 01:08:15,056
No, we'll stay at the door.
It's too dangerous.

1062
01:08:20,103 --> 01:08:22,188
You. Voice sounded familiar.

1063
01:08:22,605 --> 01:08:24,774
Mr. Vasseur. What a nice surprise.

1064
01:08:25,024 --> 01:08:26,943
Registered letter. Sign here.

1065
01:08:27,193 --> 01:08:31,239
Guess what. I speak fluent Shtimi.
I understand you now.

1066
01:08:31,489 --> 01:08:33,950
Perfect Shtimi, written and oral!

1067
01:08:34,242 --> 01:08:35,284
Let's celebrate.

1068
