Momo!

1140
01:13:17,859 --> 01:13:19,444
Four fricadelles, Momo!

1141
01:13:20,320 --> 01:13:22,196
We haven't eaten yet!

1142
01:13:24,615 --> 01:13:26,451
No! Hang on, hang on.

1143
01:13:32,582 --> 01:13:33,166
Honey?.

1144
01:13:33,458 --> 01:13:37,754
Can't come home tonight, hon.
I'm at the police station.

1145
01:13:38,046 --> 01:13:39,922
Philippe, were you mugged?

1146
01:13:40,214 --> 01:13:43,468
No. I just had
a little to drink.

1147
01:13:44,135 --> 01:13:45,428
So I got arrested.

1148
01:13:45,678 --> 01:13:46,429
In your car?

1149
01:13:46,679 --> 01:13:47,889
On a bicycle.

1150
01:13:48,181 --> 01:13:50,683
