1152
01:13:57,857 --> 01:13:59,942
Oh my darling, what's going on?

1153
01:14:00,401 --> 01:14:02,445
Don't try to drown your sorrows.

1154
01:14:03,488 --> 01:14:05,406
I know it's hard. Be strong.

1155
01:14:05,657 --> 01:14:06,699
All right.

1156
01:14:08,326 --> 01:14:11,329
