I love you.

1157
01:14:11,579 --> 01:14:13,498
Me too. More than anything.

1158
01:14:37,814 --> 01:14:38,940
Well?

1159
01:14:40,441 --> 01:14:41,567
Well what?

1160
01:14:42,443 --> 01:14:43,653
Let's see your hands.

1161
01:14:45,822 --> 01:14:48,408
No trembling. Two days sober.
No side effects?

1162
01:14:48,700 --> 01:14:49,826
I'm fine.

1163
01:14:53,246 --> 01:14:54,372
Oh no!

1164
01:14:54,664 --> 01:14:55,748
What is it?

1165
01:14:58,543 --> 01:15:01,671
You drank my perfume?
I read where alcoholics do that.

1166
01:15:01,963 --> 01:15:03,172
No, I'm holding up.

1167
01:15:03,631 --> 01:15:07,343
I'd rather go get you a bottle
than have you drink my Givenchy.

1168
01:15:19,647 --> 01:15:20,940
What's this?

1169
01:15:23,693 --> 01:15:24,610
Julie.

1170
01:15:24,861 --> 01:15:26,988
I was weak. I'm sorry.

1171
01:15:27,322 --> 01:15:28,323
What's all this?

1172
01:15:28,573 --> 01:15:30,491
My bags. I'm coming with you.

1173
01:15:31,367 --> 01:15:32,910
What about Raphael?

1174
01:15:33,369 --> 01:15:34,996
My parents will mind him.

1175
01:15:35,246 --> 01:15:37,582
We'll find him a school up north.

1176
01:15:38,124 --> 01:15:40,001
What about your store?
Your job?

1177
01:15:40,251 --> 01:15:43,212
I took a leave of absence.
I'm coming north with you.

1178
01:15:44,380 --> 01:15:45,381
No, Julie.

1179
01:15:48,176 --> 01:15:51,054
I'm scared, but I'm happy
to be going with you.

1180
01:15:51,304 --> 01:15:52,764
We'll stay together.

1181
01:15:54,849 --> 01:15:56,809
We'll be stronger together.

1182
01:16:03,608 --> 01:16:05,068
Got your seatbelt on?

1183
01:16:05,318 --> 01:16:06,569
Of course.

1184
01:16:08,237 --> 01:16:09,697
He's a maniac!

1185
01:16:31,803 --> 01:16:33,471
What speed were you doing?

1186
01:16:33,888 --> 01:16:34,639
The right one.

1187
01:16:34,931 --> 01:16:37,016
