1188
01:16:37,266 --> 01:16:38,434
My husband didn't drink.

1189
01:16:38,726 --> 01:16:40,186
He may have perfumed his mouth.

1190
01:16:40,395 --> 01:16:42,146
Don't worry.
Go with the tow truck.

1191
01:16:42,397 --> 01:16:43,231
I'm staying with you.

1192
01:16:43,439 --> 01:16:46,776
Go back, reassure everyone.
Take care of the insurance.

1193
01:16:47,026 --> 01:16:47,819
I'll take the train.

1194
01:16:48,486 --> 01:16:49,278
Good idea.

1195
01:16:49,779 --> 01:16:52,073
All right, but you be careful.

1196
01:16:52,323 --> 01:16:54,075
I'll come as soon as I can.

1197
01:16:54,325 --> 01:16:55,159
Great.

1198
01:16:56,786 --> 01:16:58,079
Come into my office.

1199
01:16:58,955 --> 01:17:00,206
We have to talk.

1200
01:17:02,083 --> 01:17:03,292
This is very serious.

1201
01:17:03,543 --> 01:17:04,419
