1204
01:17:07,296 --> 01:17:08,589
Not really.

1205
01:17:09,007 --> 01:17:11,092
- Marriage not good?
- Yes it is.

1206
01:17:12,176 --> 01:17:14,804
Since we've been 700 miles apart,
it's great.

1207
01:17:16,723 --> 01:17:18,599
My wife is depressed.

1208
01:17:19,559 --> 01:17:22,353
It helps her
to know I'm in the north.

1209
01:17:22,854 --> 01:17:25,523
She focuses on a concrete problem.

1210
01:17:27,233 --> 01:17:29,444
I'm not sure I understand.

1211
01:17:30,194 --> 01:17:31,487
I lied about you.

1212
01:17:31,904 --> 01:17:34,782
She thinks I'm in a liviing hell.
The more I suffer,

1213
01:17:35,074 --> 01:17:36,909
the better she feels.

1214
01:17:37,327 --> 01:17:38,328
Pretty twisted.

1215
01:17:38,619 --> 01:17:39,704
Maybe, but it works.

1216
01:17:39,954 --> 01:17:42,040
We have never been so happy.

1217
01:17:43,541 --> 01:17:45,543
What did you tell her about us?

1218
01:17:51,007 --> 01:17:52,342
A few clichés.

1219
01:17:52,967 --> 01:17:56,012
General notions.
I didn't make anything up.

1220
01:17:57,180 --> 01:17:59,474
I said you were a little...

1221
01:17:59,807 --> 01:18:00,892
basic.

1222
01:18:01,184 --> 01:18:02,560
A little...

1223
01:18:03,102 --> 01:18:04,395
simple,

1224
01:18:05,855 --> 01:18:07,607
a little rough.

1225
01:18:08,733 --> 01:18:10,485
At times vulgar.

1226
01:18:11,569 --> 01:18:12,862
Dense.

1227
01:18:14,447 --> 01:18:15,907
Backward, too.

1228
01:18:16,240 --> 01:18:17,992
And a few other things.

1229
01:19:00,827 --> 01:19:01,619
Hello, my love.

1230
01:19:12,255 --> 01:19:13,715
This is very pretty.

1231
01:19:14,632 --> 01:19:17,343
Honey, I have something to confess.

1232
01:19:20,346 --> 01:19:22,181
Welcome to the north, Julie!

1233
01:19:31,941 --> 01:19:32,984
