1260
01:21:34,314 --> 01:21:37,900
I tried to warn you.
I didn't want you to see this.

1261
01:21:59,380 --> 01:22:00,757
No! You live here?

1262
01:22:01,132 --> 01:22:02,050
Yes.

1263
01:22:02,300 --> 01:22:04,719
