two years?

1294
01:24:49,092 --> 01:24:51,260
How could you stand it this long?

1295
01:24:53,096 --> 01:24:54,472
I could use a drink.

1296
01:24:54,806 --> 01:24:58,726
You have to go back. I'll take you
to the train in the morning.

1297
01:24:59,769 --> 01:25:00,645
All right.

1298
01:25:01,604 --> 01:25:03,648
To get the rest of my things.

1299
01:25:03,898 --> 01:25:06,025
