1300
01:25:06,317 --> 01:25:08,987
He'll stay with my parents
2 years if necessary,

1301
01:25:09,153 --> 01:25:10,363
I'll stay with you.

1302
01:25:10,613 --> 01:25:12,115
You can't. I don't want you to.

1303
01:25:13,157 --> 01:25:16,035
I love you.
If it's your life, it's mine too.

1304
01:25:22,959 --> 01:25:23,710
Well?

1305
01:25:23,960 --> 01:25:26,004
Nothing. Maybe they're sleeping.

1306
01:25:27,005 --> 01:25:29,799
Should we finish it off
with a fire?

1307
01:25:30,508 --> 01:25:31,467
Are you crazy?.

1308
01:25:31,718 --> 01:25:32,844
You're babash.

1309
01:25:33,094 --> 01:25:35,680
