she might get suspicious.

1321
01:26:14,177 --> 01:26:16,304
Right now, I'm suspicious.

1322
01:26:18,181 --> 01:26:21,643
For once, we're together in Bergues
without my mom.

1323
01:26:24,687 --> 01:26:25,772
Good night.

1324
01:27:10,358 --> 01:27:12,193
- Did it go all right?
- No.

1325
01:27:12,986 --> 01:27:14,070
Me neither.

1326
01:27:14,278 --> 01:27:16,447
- She wants to stay.
- In the north?

1327
01:27:16,739 --> 01:27:18,116
No. Right here.

1328
01:27:20,284 --> 01:27:24,163
We dissuaded her in every way,
she's still willing to stay.

1329
01:27:24,414 --> 01:27:25,581
Why?.

1330
